Nollywood actress, Tonto Dikeh has addressed rumours that she’s a lesbian. The actress didn’t waste time to debunk the claim made by a follower. It all started after she made a post about finding out that her ex-husband was bisexual. A follower trolled her in the comment section accusing her of being a lesbian. However, she didn’t give a direct response to the question which prompted another follower to ask her to come out clean. Responding, she said that she’s as ‘straight as a ruler’. See their exchange below: Source